{"tid":1367713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方於7.21晚上接獲市民報案至趕到現場共用了39分鐘，惟未有道歉，政府是否願意道歉。張建宗隨即表示「絕對願意」","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:08:14.000Z","uid":33307,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8abc4f6e738f2384311dad3e57c6aab4e75501","tid":1367713,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"張建宗首次道歉<br />\n<br />\n記者會期間被問及，警方於7.21晚上接獲市民報案至趕到現場共用了39分鐘，惟未有道歉，政府是否願意道歉。張建宗隨即表示「絕對願意」，同時又指事件導致市民感到不快「如果想政府承擔責任，我覺得係責無旁貸」。<br />\n<br />\n記者遂再追問「會唔會同市民道歉」，張建宗則指倘市民認為警方的處理手法，與市民期望有落差「絕對願意就處理手法向市民道歉」。"},{"pid":"52987bf98a273d9e1d6326986dad10e6281050bb","tid":1367713,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:29.000Z","msg":"絕對願意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c66c994b1a95e577fe9a5a004bb36c2ba3e4f5","tid":1367713,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"標題都有聲"},{"pid":"e4a0e001ae320d7c2e3e4a0354f59aafce35c9b5","tid":1367713,"uid":289969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"Condom仔:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd3fe9525d007a2f6e82993772f2ca4f3a46af9","tid":1367713,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:40:52.000Z","msg":"願意道歉咋<br />\n都未道歉<br />\n連半跪都稱唔上<br />\n對腳屈曲小小 黑警都屌到咁<br />\n唔敢想像道歉或者成立獨立調查委員會之後會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ab1429751608d57b63c5e97d6ebeaf9446276d","tid":1367713,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4a0e001ae320d7c2e3e4a0354f59aafce35c9b5","tid":1367713,"uid":289969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"Condom仔:<img src=\"/a